WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 17]

01:52.500 --> 01:54.620
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

01:54.900 --> 01:57.060
♪As the winds rise, dragons and foxes cry in strife♪

01:57.340 --> 02:01.700
♪At the world's end, the destined soul rides proud and free♪

02:01.980 --> 02:04.100
♪I am fearless♪

02:04.340 --> 02:06.620
♪I will gather light to mend the moon for you♪

02:06.740 --> 02:08.060
♪When heaven and earth are reborn♪

02:08.180 --> 02:12.500
♪We will meet again♪

02:27.400 --> 02:28.460
The only way

02:28.460 --> 02:29.580
to destroy Jiu Ying

02:29.910 --> 02:32.020
is for each of us to devour one of its heads,

02:32.430 --> 02:33.930
then transform into mountain ranges

02:34.280 --> 02:35.580
to seal it beneath us.

02:35.910 --> 02:36.770
Chi Wen,

02:37.310 --> 02:38.790
you carry the power of sealing.

02:39.100 --> 02:40.140
The final burden

02:40.800 --> 02:41.810
falls on you.

02:42.140 --> 02:42.860
But

02:43.080 --> 02:44.210
who will seal you?

02:44.750 --> 02:46.040
What if Jiu Ying

02:46.040 --> 02:46.930
takes over your body?

02:47.470 --> 02:48.740
Don't worry, my brothers.

02:49.120 --> 02:50.250
I'll drive the Guili Sword

02:50.590 --> 02:51.580
into my dragon's spine

02:51.870 --> 02:53.140
to pin down Jiu Ying's primordial spirit.

02:53.680 --> 02:54.810
Then, I'll return to Shilin Sect,

02:54.910 --> 02:56.300
find a suitable vessel,

02:56.870 --> 02:58.060
and transfer the spirit into it

02:58.280 --> 02:59.930
using the Dragonbirth Spell,

03:00.280 --> 03:01.650
to seal away my true dragon form.

03:02.630 --> 03:03.210
After that,

03:05.000 --> 03:06.090
I'll be the one

03:06.120 --> 03:07.460
to keep the world at peace.

03:35.870 --> 03:37.690
I'm afraid a suitable vessel

03:38.030 --> 03:39.210
won't be easy to find.

03:43.310 --> 03:43.970
You're back.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.580
How was it, Chi Wen?

03:48.960 --> 03:49.580
In that case,

03:50.560 --> 03:52.090
there's only one last way.

03:53.870 --> 03:55.020
We fuse

03:55.400 --> 03:56.340
our reverse scales

03:56.750 --> 03:58.770
and create a Tenth Dragon.

03:59.680 --> 04:01.970
He will become a final hope for this world.

04:36.600 --> 04:37.300
That is me.

04:40.600 --> 04:41.420
The Tenth Dragon.

05:00.510 --> 05:01.740
Why isn't he back yet?

05:42.310 --> 05:43.010
He's fine.

05:44.070 --> 05:45.740
Take them back to Shilin Sect.

05:46.510 --> 05:46.980
Yes.

05:47.870 --> 05:48.570
Master Dragon Deity,

05:49.070 --> 05:49.890
Wu Zhiqi

05:51.040 --> 05:52.130
has a request.

05:53.240 --> 05:53.810
I know.

05:54.720 --> 05:55.540
He has mentioned it

05:56.310 --> 05:57.780
to me before.

06:00.270 --> 06:01.300
You all go ahead.

06:27.630 --> 06:28.690
Should I stay?

06:35.920 --> 06:36.930
Accompany me somewhere.

07:10.140 --> 07:12.340
♪Moonlight falters♪

07:12.940 --> 07:15.460
♪Spreading in silence♪

07:16.900 --> 07:20.380
♪Candles burn through our farewells♪

07:22.780 --> 07:24.980
♪Trapped in this body♪

07:25.660 --> 07:28.500
♪This borrowed halo♪

07:29.380 --> 07:33.460
♪Tears unshed, pain untold♪

07:38.660 --> 07:41.140
♪How pitiful, how sad♪

07:45.020 --> 07:48.620
♪Too scared to accept♪

07:50.700 --> 07:53.780
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

07:54.100 --> 07:56.940
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

07:57.300 --> 08:00.100
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

08:00.260 --> 08:02.980
♪As I drift farther away♪

08:03.500 --> 08:06.420
♪I won't wipe my tears dry♪

08:06.780 --> 08:09.580
♪Afraid the sorrow fades too light...♪

08:13.870 --> 08:14.890
Your hands are dirty.

08:16.040 --> 08:17.370
Can you really

08:18.040 --> 08:18.780
leave it unwashed?

08:27.720 --> 08:29.620
Last time I refused to wash my hands,

08:30.270 --> 08:31.220
Master Dragon Deity,

08:32.040 --> 08:33.690
you shoved my hands into the water

08:33.690 --> 08:34.570
brutally.

08:35.750 --> 08:37.020
This isn't an illusion.

08:38.390 --> 08:39.570
And I'm not Man Man.

08:42.270 --> 08:43.730
Don't test the Dragon Deity's patience.

08:46.510 --> 08:47.380
Right.

08:49.440 --> 08:51.330
You're no longer a dragon on the chopping block.

08:52.320 --> 08:53.180
What a shame.

08:55.670 --> 08:56.690
But what if

08:57.720 --> 08:59.140
I insist?

09:28.240 --> 09:28.970
If so,

09:29.480 --> 09:31.570
I'll take the ring.

09:32.240 --> 09:33.260
It's been hundreds of years,

09:34.320 --> 09:35.900
and you still act

09:36.600 --> 09:37.540
like a reckless child.

09:38.790 --> 09:39.660
If you want to try,

09:40.960 --> 09:41.930
go ahead then.

10:05.270 --> 10:07.140
You washed my hands twice before.

10:08.390 --> 10:09.140
I remember.

10:22.440 --> 10:24.300
The scent on you

10:24.750 --> 10:25.690
has faded.

10:28.900 --> 10:31.620
♪Face unseen, voice unheard♪

10:32.180 --> 10:37.300
♪Youth in twilight, a soul aging too soon...♪

10:38.320 --> 10:39.090
This handkerchief...

10:40.670 --> 10:41.690
Why do you still keep it?

10:46.220 --> 10:49.100
♪Holding those fragments♪

10:49.620 --> 10:54.460
♪Stitching up the past, piecing together tomorrow♪

10:55.020 --> 10:57.100
♪Another year has gone by♪

10:57.780 --> 11:01.740
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

11:02.220 --> 11:06.180
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

11:06.500 --> 11:09.580
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

11:10.380 --> 11:14.860
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

11:15.300 --> 11:19.180
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

11:19.620 --> 11:23.420
♪Your silence turns into my hoarse voice♪

11:23.900 --> 11:27.340
♪You left behind your final words♪

11:27.740 --> 11:34.380
♪And every word became a scar♪

13:20.910 --> 13:21.730
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

13:22.790 --> 13:23.690
Don't worry, Commander Li.

13:23.910 --> 13:25.180
He is safe.

13:25.630 --> 13:27.020
The butterfly demon has been subdued.

13:27.870 --> 13:29.660
Dragon Deity's Power on Wu Zhiqi has been reclaimed.

13:31.320 --> 13:33.140
But your body...

13:34.440 --> 13:35.090
I'm fine.

13:36.200 --> 13:36.780
Bai Ze,

13:37.910 --> 13:38.930
who exactly

13:40.000 --> 13:41.060
is Yuan Wuhuo?

13:42.150 --> 13:42.970
Master Dragon Deity,

13:43.670 --> 13:45.020
are you still thinking about the butterfly demon?

13:46.670 --> 13:47.500
Who is he?

13:49.510 --> 13:50.380
To me,

13:52.910 --> 13:53.500
he

13:57.360 --> 13:59.140
was once like a brother.

14:02.030 --> 14:02.900
Was he a dragon too?

14:05.200 --> 14:05.660
No.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.140
He was a human.

14:10.510 --> 14:12.450
Once the demon hunter commander of the Shilin Sect.

14:14.320 --> 14:15.570
He watched me grow up,

14:16.750 --> 14:17.970
and I stayed with him until the end of his life.

14:19.100 --> 14:25.740
♪How deep is the abyss? How heavy is the vow?♪

14:26.180 --> 14:28.500
♪A regret no repentance can erase♪

14:28.580 --> 14:32.540
♪Pressing against an aching heart♪

14:33.140 --> 14:40.500
♪Through countless trials and lifetimes, each of our souls♪

14:40.900 --> 14:46.220
♪Like waves, never fearing sacrifice♪

14:56.670 --> 14:57.730
When I first met him,

14:58.600 --> 14:59.690
he was a proud man.

15:00.320 --> 15:01.690
A great hero.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.020
And when I saw him off on his final journey,

15:06.150 --> 15:06.690
he was an old man

15:07.200 --> 15:08.850
worn down by illness.

15:10.790 --> 15:11.690
A mortal lifespan

15:12.720 --> 15:14.570
is the greatest shackle in this world.

15:16.510 --> 15:17.780
Since he was a human,

15:19.790 --> 15:21.450
how did he become a butterfly demon?

15:25.080 --> 15:25.850
And why

15:29.440 --> 15:31.060
does he look exactly like me?

15:33.910 --> 15:34.690
I understand now.

15:35.790 --> 15:37.140
Like Wangyan and I.

15:37.840 --> 15:39.330
Although we're not related by blood,

15:40.150 --> 15:42.140
we hold each other dear.

15:43.550 --> 15:45.730
Even knowing she's hiding something from me,

15:47.790 --> 15:49.420
I still refuse to believe it.

15:51.440 --> 15:52.500
I don't want to lose her.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.570
You won't lose her.

15:55.790 --> 15:56.850
Can you tell me

15:56.870 --> 15:58.140
what secret you're keeping with her?

15:59.390 --> 16:00.180
Tell me,

16:00.910 --> 16:02.210
and I won't lose her.

16:04.120 --> 16:05.060
I can help you too.

16:39.910 --> 16:40.930
This is the Moon Summoning Pearl.

16:42.320 --> 16:43.260
Hold it,

16:43.720 --> 16:44.780
and channel your power.

16:46.120 --> 16:47.420
No matter where I am,

16:48.390 --> 16:49.380
I'll come to you

16:49.390 --> 16:50.500
at once.

16:51.790 --> 16:52.570
Wu Wangyan.

16:55.720 --> 16:56.810
Come to me.

17:28.830 --> 17:29.460
Be careful.

17:30.030 --> 17:30.890
I can see.

17:54.550 --> 17:55.410
Shouldn't you return

17:56.030 --> 17:56.940
the Moon Summoning Pearl?

18:00.880 --> 18:01.700
Aren't you going to ask

18:03.440 --> 18:04.650
why I summoned you here?

18:05.720 --> 18:06.700
If you want to tell me,

18:07.510 --> 18:08.500
you will.

18:09.750 --> 18:10.780
If not,

18:11.400 --> 18:12.260
there's no point asking.

18:28.920 --> 18:29.680
If I hadn't used it

18:29.680 --> 18:30.610
to summon you,

18:31.310 --> 18:32.090
would you have

18:32.110 --> 18:32.940
kept avoiding me?

18:34.790 --> 18:35.890
I was just tired

18:37.960 --> 18:39.700
and wanted peace

18:40.720 --> 18:41.890
somewhere quiet.

18:43.270 --> 18:44.460
What happened in the illusion...

18:48.440 --> 18:49.020
Go ahead and ask.

18:51.510 --> 18:52.850
I'll tell you

18:53.510 --> 18:54.850
everything you want to know.

18:57.590 --> 18:58.540
Let's treat this

19:01.200 --> 19:02.260
as a final farewell.

19:13.240 --> 19:14.370
You should know,

19:14.720 --> 19:16.020
on every full moon night,

19:16.550 --> 19:18.020
all members of the Formless Moon Sect

19:18.310 --> 19:19.700
are forcibly summoned back to the Formless Moon Palace

19:20.200 --> 19:21.700
by the Power of the Moon.

19:32.440 --> 19:33.810
Once we enter the Sacred Spring,

19:34.720 --> 19:35.610
there are no secrets

19:36.400 --> 19:37.740
between us.

19:39.510 --> 19:40.700
Each rebirth

19:41.510 --> 19:42.780
reshapes the body

19:43.400 --> 19:45.220
and restores memory and emotion.

19:46.400 --> 19:47.130
One day,

19:48.680 --> 19:50.170
the Oracle Stone delivered a prophecy.

19:51.680 --> 19:52.770
We were to wipe out

19:52.770 --> 19:54.570
a village by the Blackwater River where flood dragons dwelled.

19:55.440 --> 19:56.460
I objected.

19:56.830 --> 19:57.890
We argued.

19:59.000 --> 19:59.780
Master,

20:01.160 --> 20:03.330
if there are sinners among them,

20:03.400 --> 20:04.500
punishing those responsible is enough.

20:05.070 --> 20:06.570
Why must we destroy the entire clan?

20:07.680 --> 20:10.850
The world has its balance.

20:12.000 --> 20:13.500
The Oracle Stone is never wrong.

20:14.480 --> 20:16.130
Their time is up.

20:16.830 --> 20:18.090
No one can defy fate.

20:20.680 --> 20:22.650
It was cruel to exterminate an entire clan.

20:22.960 --> 20:24.540
We all had doubts

20:25.070 --> 20:26.130
and hesitated.

20:26.750 --> 20:28.220
We didn't act immediately.

20:28.550 --> 20:30.130
But when we woke again,

20:31.400 --> 20:32.260
my memory

20:33.160 --> 20:34.460
had reset to the last time

20:34.550 --> 20:36.020
I entered the Sacred Spring.

20:36.480 --> 20:38.460
It happened to everyone.

20:39.830 --> 20:40.500
We

20:41.880 --> 20:42.740
had been reborn.

21:08.680 --> 21:10.170
Master,

21:10.310 --> 21:11.980
thank you for granting us new life.

21:15.480 --> 21:17.060
Xie Lingxi killed you.

21:20.110 --> 21:21.130
But he didn't know

21:23.000 --> 21:24.090
the Power of the Moon

21:25.590 --> 21:26.890
grants us eternal life.

21:32.510 --> 21:33.500
The Fox Queen never mentioned

21:33.500 --> 21:34.460
that mission again.

21:35.160 --> 21:36.940
As if it had never happened.

21:38.480 --> 21:40.370
Even the memory of our argument and the mission

21:40.590 --> 21:42.570
was never stored in the Primordial Sacred Spring.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.500
No one remembered.

21:47.920 --> 21:49.700
I went back alone to the Blackwater River.

21:51.550 --> 21:52.980
No one survived.

21:54.960 --> 21:55.890
But traces of my power

21:56.350 --> 21:58.020
were everywhere.

22:02.830 --> 22:03.740
That was

22:04.350 --> 22:06.500
when I realized I had committed slaughter.

22:08.110 --> 22:09.650
But I didn't know

22:09.960 --> 22:10.980
they were the flood dragons.

22:12.000 --> 22:13.780
Only after entering the Star Stone

22:14.680 --> 22:16.410
did my memories slowly return.

22:18.070 --> 22:19.700
That was when

22:21.400 --> 22:22.370
I understood

22:23.720 --> 22:26.060
that the Fox Queen's consciousness had never awakened.

22:26.750 --> 22:28.000
The one controlling us

22:28.000 --> 22:29.020
through the Oracle Stone

22:30.350 --> 22:31.850
- was actually... - It was Jiu Ying.

22:33.920 --> 22:34.410
Yes.

22:36.880 --> 22:38.330
Jiu Ying used the Oracle Stone

22:38.920 --> 22:40.170
to control the Formless Moon Sect.

22:42.640 --> 22:44.020
I was under his control too.

22:44.920 --> 22:46.020
I had no choice.

22:46.680 --> 22:48.740
Even now, you're still lying to me.

22:49.880 --> 22:51.130
You said you lost your memories

22:51.310 --> 22:52.540
after rebirth.

22:53.030 --> 22:54.220
Then how do you remember all this?

22:55.200 --> 22:57.170
If Jiu Ying erased your memories,

22:57.400 --> 22:58.590
he wouldn't leave any clues

22:58.590 --> 22:59.500
for you to discover.

23:13.510 --> 23:15.060
Your brother helped me.

23:17.400 --> 23:18.170
My brother?

23:18.960 --> 23:19.850
Your brother,

23:20.680 --> 23:21.370
the Ninth Dragon,

23:22.270 --> 23:23.020
Chi Wen.

23:23.830 --> 23:25.410
Master Chi Wen left you a message.

23:25.720 --> 23:27.300
The Oracle Stone can't be trusted.

23:27.830 --> 23:28.940
If you have doubts,

23:29.880 --> 23:30.780
seal part of your memories

23:30.780 --> 23:32.130
inside this artifact.

23:33.270 --> 23:34.300
Retrieve them later,

23:35.240 --> 23:36.170
and they'll remind you of the truth.

23:38.200 --> 23:39.780
Among all the sisters in the Formless Moon Sect,

23:40.510 --> 23:41.300
I'm the only one

23:41.440 --> 23:43.220
who still remembers the massacre.

23:43.790 --> 23:44.740
Perhaps because

23:44.740 --> 23:46.130
I doubted and resisted,

23:47.270 --> 23:49.330
Jiu Ying chose me as his vessel.

23:50.400 --> 23:51.020
After that,

23:51.880 --> 23:52.650
I didn't dare let him sense

23:52.680 --> 23:53.780
anything unusual.

23:54.440 --> 23:56.060
Before entering the Sacred Spring,

23:57.070 --> 23:58.070
I would always seal away

23:58.070 --> 23:59.370
any memories or emotions

23:59.480 --> 24:00.570
that might expose me.

24:04.160 --> 24:06.060
Any memories or emotions that might expose you?

24:13.030 --> 24:14.060
Does that include me?

24:28.550 --> 24:29.540
I suppose

24:31.030 --> 24:32.170
that answer

24:33.480 --> 24:34.570
doesn't matter to you anymore.

24:40.680 --> 24:41.980
So you never intended

24:42.000 --> 24:43.220
to carry out the dragon-slaying plan.

24:44.640 --> 24:46.090
Saying you'd slay the dragon with me

24:47.110 --> 24:48.170
was a lie.

24:49.680 --> 24:51.060
You and Chi Wen

24:51.110 --> 24:51.980
planned all this together.

24:53.880 --> 24:54.460
Right?

24:55.200 --> 24:55.810
That's right.

24:57.720 --> 24:58.850
He told me to stay close to you

24:59.920 --> 25:01.410
and find a way to get the prayer bead bracelet.

25:02.590 --> 25:03.650
You and Chi Wen

25:04.350 --> 25:05.650
share the same dragon lineage,

25:05.680 --> 25:06.810
yet you're strangers to each other.

25:07.830 --> 25:08.700
Fate

25:09.830 --> 25:11.090
has been cruel.

25:15.240 --> 25:16.780
So you stayed by my side

25:17.510 --> 25:18.980
for the prayer bead bracelet.

25:20.590 --> 25:21.330
I thought...

25:23.200 --> 25:23.940
I thought...

25:34.720 --> 25:36.370
The Twelve thoughts weren't found in the illusion.

25:36.960 --> 25:38.020
You couldn't succeed.

25:43.070 --> 25:44.810
But I gained something there too.

25:47.440 --> 25:49.260
Something I never expected.

25:51.830 --> 25:52.780
And just as quickly,

25:53.720 --> 25:55.090
I lost it.

25:58.350 --> 25:59.850
Hasn't the boy returned yet?

26:00.720 --> 26:02.260
He went for training with his master.

26:02.750 --> 26:03.570
He'll be back tomorrow.

26:04.790 --> 26:05.220
Here.

26:06.110 --> 26:07.300
Try the water. Is it too hot?

26:07.640 --> 26:08.020
Here.

26:15.200 --> 26:15.740
Is it too hot?

26:20.720 --> 26:21.370
You shouldn't

26:21.640 --> 26:23.090
stay cooped up all day.

26:23.550 --> 26:24.540
Your legs are getting weak.

26:25.830 --> 26:26.810
I'll take you out for a walk.

26:27.310 --> 26:28.370
Go do your work.

26:28.920 --> 26:29.740
Don't worry about me.

26:30.790 --> 26:31.940
In this illusion,

26:32.400 --> 26:33.500
you're the only one who's real.

26:34.350 --> 26:35.300
Everything else is fake.

26:36.160 --> 26:37.060
So what's the point of dealing with them?

26:37.880 --> 26:39.020
I'm not real either.

26:43.030 --> 26:43.940
Or do you really think

26:45.640 --> 26:47.330
I'm your wife?

26:48.700 --> 26:50.780
♪A gentle frown♪

26:51.180 --> 26:55.060
♪So many words I swallow in the end...♪

26:55.590 --> 26:57.090
Time can be erased.

26:57.680 --> 26:58.850
Memories too.

26:59.590 --> 27:00.980
Would you do that?

27:03.270 --> 27:04.940
Would you forget

27:06.110 --> 27:07.220
the truth you've just learned,

27:08.240 --> 27:10.810
and return to the peaceful life we once had?

27:13.640 --> 27:15.540
That peaceful life over those past decades

27:16.830 --> 27:17.980
belongs to my parents.

27:19.070 --> 27:19.850
Not to you.

27:22.070 --> 27:23.220
And not to us.

27:29.580 --> 27:34.980
♪At break of dawn, someone will remember her♪

27:35.460 --> 27:41.580
♪Time whispers its vow, like water flowing by...♪

27:43.030 --> 27:44.980
You can't let go of the hatred,

27:46.070 --> 27:48.260
and I can't wash the blood from my hands.

27:50.720 --> 27:51.370
So

27:53.030 --> 27:53.850
let me go.

27:57.240 --> 27:58.650
Let yourself go too.

27:59.530 --> 28:00.580
Let him go.

28:00.750 --> 28:02.100
And let us be free, alright?

28:02.100 --> 28:06.020
♪Waiting for the final night before sunset♪

28:06.140 --> 28:09.100
♪Let everything left behind♪

28:09.460 --> 28:11.060
♪Ask nothing of this world♪

28:11.220 --> 28:14.900
♪No more delusions, no more words♪

28:18.680 --> 28:19.850
Is Wu Shiguang

28:24.030 --> 28:26.000
really the Tenth Dragon?

28:29.830 --> 28:31.090
And Master Dragon Deity...

28:32.270 --> 28:33.460
Everything happens as it should.

28:33.960 --> 28:35.090
The ending is written in the star.

28:36.070 --> 28:37.090
We know that,

28:38.240 --> 28:38.780
don't we?

28:47.750 --> 28:48.890
I should get going.

28:51.790 --> 28:52.740
It's the full moon tonight.

28:53.510 --> 28:54.500
I have to return.

29:16.640 --> 29:18.810
Going home should be a good thing.

29:19.920 --> 29:20.940
Why do you look sad?

29:25.920 --> 29:26.940
Once I return to the Formless Moon Sect

29:27.920 --> 29:29.370
and enter the Primordial Sacred Spring,

29:31.070 --> 29:32.410
everything you and Wangyan planned

29:33.480 --> 29:34.940
will be exposed to the Fox Queen.

29:36.110 --> 29:37.260
If you don't share your memory...

29:39.680 --> 29:40.850
Will you tell her?

29:45.310 --> 29:46.170
I don't know.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.370
I don't want to betray the Formless Moon Sect.

29:55.790 --> 29:56.940
But I understand

29:57.960 --> 29:59.410
why Wangyan wanted to leave.

30:01.400 --> 30:02.610
When you've been bound for too long,

30:05.830 --> 30:06.700
you start wanting to break free.

30:09.350 --> 30:11.700
Everyone's the same.

30:13.030 --> 30:14.020
You can change your face, reshape your body,

30:15.000 --> 30:16.020
but the heart is the hardest thing to disguise.

30:18.030 --> 30:19.170
When you long for something

30:21.200 --> 30:22.460
but can't go after it,

30:25.750 --> 30:26.740
that's the saddest thing of all.

30:29.550 --> 30:30.330
Just like

30:30.720 --> 30:32.300
when you killed that child.

30:33.480 --> 30:35.220
You knew it had to be done,

30:36.440 --> 30:39.980
but seeing your hands covered in blood

30:41.640 --> 30:42.940
still hurts,

30:44.510 --> 30:45.060
doesn't it?

30:50.920 --> 30:51.980
Why are you crying?

30:56.070 --> 30:56.850
You knew.

30:59.590 --> 31:00.940
You knew everything.

31:02.000 --> 31:03.980
You knew I hate getting my hands dirty.

31:04.480 --> 31:06.170
You knew I liked everlasting flowers.

31:09.270 --> 31:10.850
You even knew I'm Hui.

31:15.270 --> 31:16.300
But those things,

31:19.550 --> 31:20.810
only Ji Ling knew.

31:21.550 --> 31:22.610
Next time we meet,

31:22.790 --> 31:24.130
I'll make you a flower

31:24.130 --> 31:25.260
that will never wither.

31:25.750 --> 31:26.300
Would you like that?

31:26.680 --> 31:27.810
My love for Di Zhu

31:28.200 --> 31:30.170
is like that beautiful everlasting flower.

31:30.720 --> 31:31.650
It will never fade.

31:33.030 --> 31:34.330
Because my moon phase

31:35.480 --> 31:36.170
is Hui.

31:36.790 --> 31:38.890
When you can't see the moon at night,

31:39.400 --> 31:40.370
that moon phase

31:40.880 --> 31:41.570
is Hui.

31:42.270 --> 31:43.740
The sky is pitch black.

31:44.070 --> 31:44.940
There's no moon.

31:45.830 --> 31:46.330
There is.

31:48.070 --> 31:49.020
It's called Hui.

31:50.270 --> 31:52.020
Did you devour Ji Ling

31:54.480 --> 31:55.980
and inherit his memory?

32:00.830 --> 32:01.980
Or

32:07.110 --> 32:08.300
are you Ji Ling?

32:14.720 --> 32:16.090
If it's the former,

32:19.750 --> 32:20.700
what would you do?

32:23.590 --> 32:24.500
I'd hate you.

32:31.270 --> 32:32.650
I'd hate myself too.

32:42.550 --> 32:43.540
Then,

32:44.820 --> 32:45.890
if it's the latter?

32:49.920 --> 32:50.780
Then I...

32:57.020 --> 33:02.540
♪They say if we loved once before♪

33:03.740 --> 33:06.820
♪Even apart, we still feel it all♪

33:07.660 --> 33:15.220
♪Like thousands of blooms on that shore♪

33:17.220 --> 33:21.940
♪At last, the moment is here♪

33:22.900 --> 33:29.580
♪You smile at me, but it's bittersweet♪

33:30.700 --> 33:34.780
♪Hand in hand, we'd sit close, quietly♪

34:10.340 --> 34:12.260
♪Sands in the snow♪

34:12.780 --> 34:16.620
♪Stain whose flawless white...♪

34:16.800 --> 34:18.130
Perhaps before long,

34:20.280 --> 34:21.940
you'll end up like me.

34:25.000 --> 34:26.060
Don't become like me.

34:28.030 --> 34:28.860
It's not worth it.

34:31.170 --> 34:36.580
♪At break of dawn, someone will remember her♪

34:43.800 --> 34:45.980
It's been so long since I last saw his face.

34:46.760 --> 34:47.540
Lately,

34:47.800 --> 34:49.540
I keep thinking about when he was a kid.

34:51.710 --> 34:53.770
The first time he called me "Mother".

34:55.030 --> 34:55.940
So tiny.

34:57.360 --> 34:58.940
His voice melted my heart.

35:00.480 --> 35:01.420
And someone

35:02.880 --> 35:04.900
was getting flustered with jealousy.

35:05.670 --> 35:07.020
Do you remember?

35:07.360 --> 35:08.770
He had a high fever in the middle of the night.

35:09.630 --> 35:10.820
I said he'd be fine,

35:11.800 --> 35:13.380
but you insisted on taking him out

35:13.510 --> 35:14.650
to find a physician.

35:15.150 --> 35:15.860
You even gathered

35:15.860 --> 35:16.980
every physician

35:16.980 --> 35:17.940
in the village.

35:19.070 --> 35:21.090
Someone was even jealous of himself.

35:25.800 --> 35:27.170
Even knowing it was an illusion,

35:28.030 --> 35:29.090
after so long,

35:30.190 --> 35:31.610
I still got drawn into it.

35:34.070 --> 35:35.090
You don't want to stay here.

35:36.590 --> 35:37.610
For me,

35:38.480 --> 35:39.230
I get to see my late brother

35:39.230 --> 35:40.570
every day.

35:42.360 --> 35:43.500
But you're different.

35:46.880 --> 35:48.380
You're trapped

35:48.880 --> 35:50.130
in an illusory life

35:50.150 --> 35:51.210
that has nothing to do with you.

35:56.630 --> 35:57.980
You've worn it for years.

35:59.670 --> 36:00.860
I was thinking...

36:02.000 --> 36:02.730
Are you all right?

36:02.730 --> 36:04.130
Before my eyesight gets worse,

36:04.670 --> 36:06.130
I'd make you a new one.

36:06.630 --> 36:07.210
It's fine.

36:08.070 --> 36:09.060
I like this one.

36:10.510 --> 36:12.540
This bracelet means forever.

36:13.760 --> 36:14.940
If it breaks, it's a bad omen.

36:16.960 --> 36:18.090
It should be kept safe,

36:19.230 --> 36:20.250
not worn every day

36:20.670 --> 36:21.650
as I do.

36:23.840 --> 36:24.540
So

36:27.880 --> 36:28.940
you knew it all along.

36:34.840 --> 36:35.820
Instead of putting it away,

36:37.320 --> 36:38.380
I'd rather wear it.

36:39.670 --> 36:40.460
Every time I see it,

36:41.920 --> 36:43.250
I can't help but wonder.

36:45.840 --> 36:47.420
Have you started to like this place?

36:50.150 --> 36:51.130
We've both changed.

36:52.670 --> 36:53.570
And yet,

36:54.440 --> 36:55.320
it feels like

36:55.320 --> 36:56.250
this is who we were meant to be.

37:02.440 --> 37:04.340
That's why I hoped it would break.

37:06.110 --> 37:07.420
Because no matter how much we like it,

37:08.440 --> 37:10.730
this life doesn't belong to us.

37:12.320 --> 37:13.860
Like something stolen,

37:15.150 --> 37:16.210
even if you love it,

37:18.480 --> 37:19.980
it never sits right in your heart.

37:21.670 --> 37:23.540
Then why make me a new one?

37:24.630 --> 37:25.650
Over and over again.

37:26.440 --> 37:27.170
Isn't that tiring?

37:28.880 --> 37:30.020
When you crouch too long in the dark,

37:30.880 --> 37:32.130
you start to crave warmth.

37:33.440 --> 37:34.500
And once you crave it,

37:35.000 --> 37:36.500
you do foolish things.

37:39.360 --> 37:40.770
There are many people

37:41.670 --> 37:43.210
who are full of contradictions.

37:44.110 --> 37:45.210
Maybe that's why

37:45.920 --> 37:47.130
even the smartest

37:47.670 --> 37:49.420
can do the most foolish things.

37:50.550 --> 37:51.730
Love

37:51.920 --> 37:53.460
can make someone

37:53.510 --> 37:54.460
put down their blade.

37:54.910 --> 37:57.130
Make the proud bow their head.

37:58.190 --> 37:59.540
Make the sharpest mind

37:59.800 --> 38:01.800
to do the most foolish things.

38:08.960 --> 38:09.730
And you?

38:11.400 --> 38:13.090
Staying here with me and doing all these foolish things,

38:14.000 --> 38:14.860
aren't you tired?

38:16.460 --> 38:22.500
♪A face worn old by wind, snow, and frost♪

38:23.540 --> 38:27.820
♪The opening of the story is but a blank line...♪

38:27.840 --> 38:28.540
Me?

38:30.510 --> 38:31.980
Maybe I'm just selfish.

38:33.710 --> 38:35.090
I'd rather we suffer together

38:35.630 --> 38:37.290
than be left alone.

38:38.540 --> 38:40.580
♪Eyes brim with tears...♪

38:45.360 --> 38:46.580
You're the fool.

38:46.580 --> 38:52.980
♪Watch the spring breeze stir the warm sun, flowers across the hills...♪

38:55.920 --> 38:56.770
All of this

38:57.630 --> 38:59.250
will end someday.

39:00.280 --> 39:00.730
Yes.

39:02.190 --> 39:03.290
Once we learn the truth,

39:04.510 --> 39:05.420
we'll leave.

39:07.000 --> 39:07.770
When that time comes,

39:10.230 --> 39:11.090
could you

39:12.630 --> 39:13.860
make me another bracelet?

39:15.320 --> 39:16.090
One that's stronger.

39:17.840 --> 39:19.130
One I can wear for a lifetime.

39:24.620 --> 39:30.660
♪With hair gone white, we softly recount the story...♪

39:31.840 --> 39:32.380
Sure.

39:37.380 --> 39:42.140
♪Moon, oh moon, why veil your light in frost?♪

39:42.580 --> 39:48.180
♪In my dreams, she leans by the window, lost♪

39:49.060 --> 39:54.380
♪In the tide, longing drifts and flows♪

39:55.180 --> 40:00.700
♪From afar, is it you singing soft and low?♪

40:04.580 --> 40:07.580
♪Don't forget, don't forget♪

40:07.780 --> 40:10.660
♪Let the moonlight gently sway♪

40:10.820 --> 40:13.460
♪Ripples dance in silver glow♪

40:13.460 --> 40:16.820
♪A harbor warm from yesterday♪

40:16.940 --> 40:19.780
♪Hair turns white in time's flow♪

40:20.020 --> 40:22.820
♪You rest upon my shoulder♪

40:23.020 --> 40:27.100
♪Take me back where we belong♪

40:29.740 --> 40:34.540
♪Moon, oh moon, paint my cheeks so red♪

40:34.940 --> 40:40.700
♪Light my path through the crowds ahead♪

40:41.340 --> 40:46.780
♪In my dreams, I hear you softly whisper♪

40:47.500 --> 40:54.100
♪This fleeting moment we can't reclaim♪

40:54.940 --> 40:59.740
♪Moon, oh moon, paint my cheeks so red♪

41:00.140 --> 41:05.900
♪Light my path through the crowds ahead♪

41:06.540 --> 41:11.980
♪In my dreams, I hear you softly whisper♪

41:12.700 --> 41:20.460
♪This fleeting moment we can't reclaim♪

41:30.920 --> 41:31.460
Stop it.

41:45.230 --> 41:46.130
What are you doing?

41:49.150 --> 41:49.820
What about you?

41:53.480 --> 41:54.540
What are you doing here?

41:54.800 --> 41:55.770
Will severing your own tail really help?

41:56.590 --> 41:57.860
Xiaowei was always on the run,

41:57.860 --> 41:59.170
hunted by the Never-Ending Curse.

41:59.800 --> 42:01.460
And you'll lose all your senses.

42:03.480 --> 42:05.020
Going blind again doesn't scare me.

42:06.710 --> 42:07.940
I'm used to it.

42:10.630 --> 42:11.540
All these years,

42:14.110 --> 42:15.380
you've been by my side.

42:19.630 --> 42:20.570
I've grown used to that too.

42:26.590 --> 42:27.730
Let me face this with you.

42:29.280 --> 42:30.570
I have to face it alone.

42:33.230 --> 42:34.860
Tonight is the full moon.

42:36.150 --> 42:37.570
Everyone from the Formless Moon Sect,

42:39.440 --> 42:40.460
including Jiu Ying,

42:42.670 --> 42:44.980
will find out the secret between Chi Wen and me.

42:45.710 --> 42:46.770
Other than severing my tail,

42:47.230 --> 42:48.690
I have no choice.

42:49.670 --> 42:51.060
All I can do is admit defeat.

42:52.590 --> 42:53.130
Wangyan,

42:53.760 --> 42:55.340
this was all Jiu Ying's scheme.

42:56.320 --> 42:56.860
Don't be afraid.

42:57.630 --> 42:58.570
Don't hide.

42:59.670 --> 43:00.340
I'm here.

43:01.880 --> 43:02.860
I'll always stay with you.

43:06.630 --> 43:07.210
All right?

43:11.110 --> 43:12.340
It's too late.

43:16.400 --> 43:17.290
Too late.

43:18.030 --> 43:18.540
Tonight...

43:18.920 --> 43:19.730
I know.

43:20.670 --> 43:21.500
I know everything.

43:22.920 --> 43:24.250
Tonight is the full moon.

43:25.030 --> 43:26.610
I can't stop them from summoning you back.

43:29.550 --> 43:30.380
But believe me.

43:33.280 --> 43:34.340
I will come find you.

43:36.150 --> 43:36.770
Wait for me.

43:38.230 --> 43:39.570
I'll bring you back, no matter what.

43:39.820 --> 43:46.300
♪I walk into a heartbreak burning bright♪

43:46.620 --> 43:53.500
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft♪

43:53.580 --> 43:56.700
♪Tears slowly turn to frost♪

43:57.060 --> 44:00.660
♪Fading to white, all is lost♪

44:00.940 --> 44:08.220
♪When I wake, who's by my side?♪

44:23.300 --> 44:29.780
♪If you're a kite, drifting in the world♪

44:30.700 --> 44:36.620
♪I'd be the waves, just to carry you away♪

44:37.060 --> 44:43.420
♪Too late we met, yet the stars keep me awake♪

44:44.300 --> 44:51.700
♪The wind drifts by, leaves a lonely light. You and I stay, without a word tonight♪

44:53.540 --> 44:59.620
♪If you're a snow mountain, sleeping in winter♪

45:00.860 --> 45:06.580
♪I'll be the dusk glow on your peak♪

45:07.060 --> 45:13.540
♪As time drifts by like smoke, youth fades into silver hair♪

45:14.500 --> 45:20.580
♪The love I leave for you, let heaven and earth bear witness♪

45:21.860 --> 45:28.180
♪I am a little fish, yet you never cast your net♪

45:29.020 --> 45:35.260
♪I am a wild horse, yet you dare let me run free♪

45:36.140 --> 45:41.980
♪You gently guard every moment I'm lost♪

45:42.860 --> 45:49.260
♪The world is vast, where will you settle?♪

45:50.220 --> 45:56.180
♪If you're a little boat, I'll be your mast♪

45:57.060 --> 46:03.660
♪You are a painting, beautiful even without color♪

46:04.420 --> 46:10.300
♪I miss the furrow between your brows so true♪

46:11.180 --> 46:17.620
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

46:18.340 --> 46:24.540
♪If you're a little boat, I'll be the shore♪

46:25.460 --> 46:31.660
♪Holding your weariness and all your joys and sorrows♪

46:32.540 --> 46:38.460
♪I truly cherish the sweetness in your smile♪

46:39.300 --> 46:45.100
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪
